title: Brave Saint Saturn Discography 2000-2008 (3 Releases)
description:
----------------------------------------------------------------
BRAVE SAINT SATURN DISCOGRAPHY
----------------------------------------------------------------

This Brave Saint Saturn discography may or may not be complete.  It includes the following 3 releases...

 * 2000 - So Far From Home
 * 2003 - The Light Of Things Hoped For
 * 2008 - Anti-Meridian

Brave Saint Saturn is a Christian rock band formed in Denver, Colorado in 1999. The band is a side-project of former members of Five Iron Frenzy started by Reese Roper. The band calls their music style "astro-rock," although Reese has stated that this "doesn't mean anything." The trilogy of albums are meant to artfully represent early life, adversity, and death.

God Bless,
TorrentTracts - November 2012
